asset.hookText: Nick Garcia kicks off the new backpack and skateboard collection. The Element team is constantly on the road discovering new spots, cities and cultures. With this in mind, our design team has taken each riders style and needs into consideration to complete a new line of bags, alongside new boards. We're also offering a patch pack with any bag purchase to personalize your new bag.
